Stylish Free Standing 3 Bedroom Townhouse With Full Ensuite & Good Size Back Yard In TOP LOCATION!
Beautiful inside and out! A RARE opportunity to own this stylish 3 bedroom Townhouse. With its own street front, favourable open plan living with an abundance of natural lighting, WW carpets and floorboards we guarantee you won't be disappointed.
Complete with large bedrooms including built in robes, full ensuite and walk in robe to master bedroom, upstairs bathroom with shower and bath, SEP. Come and inspect and MAKE US YOUR OFFER NOW.

Description:
Endless Options in Comprehensive Development Zone (SCH2)
This is a blank canvas for any developer, investor or business owner in an unbeatable location. A vacant block of land of 558 sqm (approx.) with an 18.10 meter frontage allowing for the development of a commercial premises, residential building or mixture of both.
Sitting within the Comprehensive Development Zone (SCH2) of the Greater Dandenong Planning Scheme, the precinct encourages street front retail and greater diversity of use including mixture of commercial use at ground level with offices, and accommodation above to create 24 hour activity.
The vacant allotment gives possibility to build up to 5 storeys (STPA) and has rear laneway access suitable for car parking entrance.
Highly accessible to all major amenities including Dandenong Railway Station, Dandenong Market and Plaza, major roads including Dandenong Bypass and Eastlink Freeway as well as ability for any development to overlook entire Dandenong CBD and potentially new stadium as part of Dandenong’s push for an A-League team this allotment is perfectly positioned to take advantage of Dandenong’s fast growing landscape.
Do not miss out on this truly unique and potentially once in a lifetime opportunity. You may not find another one like it.
Contact: Neb Delibasic on 0411 332 467
AUCTION: THURSDAY 25TH OCTOBER 2018 AT 1:00PM, ON SITE
TERMS: 10% DEPOSIT, BALANCE IN 30-90 DAYS
TO VIEW THE CONSUMER AFFAIRS DUE DILIGENCE CHECKLIST PLEASE VISIT http://www.consumer.vic.gov.au/duediligencechecklist

Description:
Beautifully presented in a highly sought after location!
Harcourts Dandenong is proud to introduce this renovated 2 bedroom unit in the heart of Dandenong. Whether you are looking to get into the market, downsizing or looking for a savvy investment, this is a great move!
Built to last, this classic hardwood framed brick veneer features:
- 2 generously sized bedrooms with BIR
- renovated kitchen and bathroom with oversized shower
- appealing vintage features such as box sash windows and brick feature wall
- onsite undercover car park with large storage cage
- low maintenance backyard
Additional features of this elevated property include dual fuel cooking, open plan lounge and dining, full size laundry and ample attic storage. Located on a quiet street within walking distance to Dandenong Plaza, public transport, schools, recreational grounds and natural wetlands, and only a 5 minute drive to the Monash Freeway and Eastlink.
With an abundance of natural light, this property brings a refreshing glow to everyday life. Call Patrick on 0449 616 186 to book an inspection before it's sold!

Description:
Spacious Apartment in Central Dandenong
Set five minutes from Dandenong Central with dining, retail, parks and markets all within a short walk or minutes drive, this bright, spacious, fully renovated two bedroom apartment will appeal to owner occupiers and investors alike.
Much more than your standard apartment, this top floor, secure apartment blends it's private, peaceful position with lifestyle practicality.
With not a thing to do but enjoy, the apartment is filled with plenty of storage, the ideally designed floor plan features an entry hall, light filled kitchen/dining area with plenty of cupboard space, an inviting living room, two double bedrooms with built in robes, bathroom with laundry, separate powder room and undercover parking gives you everything you need and completes the home.
Extras include quality floating floors throughout with tiles to wet areas, new vertical window furnishings, split system air-con heating in lounge, downlights throughout, tiled shower base and plenty more.
With a bus stop at your door, a short walking distance to Dandenong TAFE, schools and medical clinics and a hop, skip and a jump to Dandenong Market and Dandenong Plaza, everything you need for easy living is at your doorstep.
Call for your private inspection.

Description:
CONTEMPORARY & LOW MAINTENANCE LIVING!!
This lovely home suits all First Home Buyers, Downsizers, Upsizing and Astute investors. Situated in a quiet pocket of the well-regarded Metro Village Estate and only within a short walking distance to all that Dandenong has to offer. This home provides a convenient and low maintenance lifestyle for all.
The Ground Floor offers a spacious open plan living zone, dining/meals area which is adjacent to the lovely kitchen equipped with Caesar Stone benches, S/S appliances, gas cooking, dishwasher and an abundance of cupboard space. Also featuring on the ground floor is a powder room, laundry, storage space and a fourth Bedroom with BIR or second living zone make up the rest of the ground floor. Enjoy all year round entertaining in the lovely backyard featuring a spacious pergola, low maintenance garden and play area
The First Floor of this home is carpeted throughout and possesses three extra-large bedrooms all with BIR's, master with a humongous ensuite and study nook the bathroom and separate toilet make up the rest of the first floor.
Features of this home also include: ducted heating, split system, double garage with drive through access.
Located close by to the Dandenong Station, Eastlink/Monash Freeway, Dandenong Plaza/Market, train station, public transport, recreational facilities and so much more. There are no excuses for missing out on this home.
Call Ben Jusufi or Burak Gul for any further questions!

Description:
The Desire of All Dandenong!!!
Enviably situated in the coveted Metro Village Estate, the immediate appeal of this modern residence is more than matched by the spacious interiors that brilliantly showcase the home's allure with a contemporary floorplan. This immaculate haven has an inviting Open Plan Living with ample kitchen cabinets and pantries, a separate dining area and a spacious second living area.
The Master bedroom is carefully tucked away on the upper floor with an extra-large Walk in Robe and a double vanity Ensuite. Upper floor also presents 3 good sized bedrooms with spacious WIRs, with 2 separate toilet, powder room downstairs and a main bathroom featuring a bathtub.
A remote-controlled double garage and a private easy maintenance courtyard is ideal for families. A delightful surprise package, it also includes ducted heating and evaporative cooling throughout, air-conditioning on the master bedroom with four extra linden space for your storage.
Desirably situated opposite the Dandenong Station, within short walking distance to the retail precinct like Dandenong Plaza and Market, local businesses, pre-schools, primary schools, high schools and an abundance of multicultural eateries. Commuting to the city is made easy with Eastlink and Princes Highway close by and Public Transport is within reach.
